de.uni_hildesheim.sse.qmApp

Class ConfigurableElement

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.uni_hildesheim.sse.qmApp.ConfigurableElement

  • public class ConfigurableElement
extends java.lang.Object
    Class manages a list of configurable elements which we populate in order to show these elements in the View of the QualiMaster-App. Using a given configuration we populate this list with machines, specialized Hardware, pipelines. Moreover this class provides methods to manipulate this list. Thus it is possible to remove certain elements from the list.
    Author:
    Niko Nowatzki, Holger Eichelberger
